#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:1
msgid "TOML API"
msgstr "TOML API"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:3
msgid ""
"TOML parsing and editing helpers are available under `ptool.toml` and "
"`p.toml`."
msgstr "TOML 解析与编辑辅助能力位于 `ptool.toml` 和 `p.toml` 下。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:5
msgid "ptool.toml.parse"
msgstr "ptool.toml.parse"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:7
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:7"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:9
msgid "`ptool.toml.parse(input)` parses a TOML string into a Lua table."
msgstr "`ptool.toml.parse(input)` 将 TOML 字符串解析为 Lua 表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:11
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:11"
msgid "`input` (string, required): The TOML text."
msgstr "`input`（string，必填）：TOML 文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:12
msgid "Returns: A Lua table (the root node is always a table)."
msgstr "返回：Lua 表（根节点始终是 table）。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:14
msgid "Type mapping:"
msgstr "类型映射："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:16
msgid "TOML table / inline table -> Lua table"
msgstr "TOML table / inline table -> Lua table"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:17
msgid "TOML array -> Lua sequence table (1-based)"
msgstr "TOML array -> Lua 序列表（从 1 开始）"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:18
msgid "TOML string -> Lua string"
msgstr "TOML string -> Lua string"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:19
msgid "TOML integer -> Lua integer"
msgstr "TOML integer -> Lua integer"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:20
msgid "TOML float -> Lua number"
msgstr "TOML float -> Lua number"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:21
msgid "TOML boolean -> Lua boolean"
msgstr "TOML boolean -> Lua boolean"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:22
msgid "TOML datetime/date/time -> Lua string"
msgstr "TOML datetime/date/time -> Lua string"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:24
msgid "Error behavior:"
msgstr "错误行为："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:26
msgid "An error is raised if `input` is not a string."
msgstr "如果 `input` 不是字符串，会抛出错误。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:27
msgid ""
"A TOML syntax error raises an error whose message includes line and column "
"information."
msgstr "如果 TOML 语法有误，会抛出错误，错误信息中包含行号和列号。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:30
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:30"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:41
msgid "ptool.toml.get"
msgstr "ptool.toml.get"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:43
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:43"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:43
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:43"
msgid "`v0.4.0` - Added numeric path segments for array indexing."
msgstr "`v0.4.0` - 新增数组索引用的数字路径段。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:47
msgid ""
"`ptool.toml.get(input, path)` reads the value at a specified path from TOML "
"text."
msgstr "`ptool.toml.get(input, path)` 从 TOML 文本中读取指定路径上的值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:50
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:50"
msgid "`input` (string, required): The TOML text."
msgstr "`input`（string，必填）：TOML 文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:51
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:51"
msgid ""
"`path` ((string|integer)[], required): A non-empty path array, such as `{"
"\"package\", \"version\"}` or `{\"bin\", 1, \"name\"}`."
msgstr ""
"`path`（(string|integer)[]，必填）：非空路径数组，例如 `{\"package\", "
"\"version\"}` 或 `{\"bin\", 1, \"name\"}`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:53
msgid ""
"Returns: The corresponding Lua value, or `nil` if the path does not exist."
msgstr "返回：对应的 Lua 值；如果路径不存在，则返回 `nil`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:55
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:55"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:57
msgid "String path segments select table keys."
msgstr "字符串路径段用于选择 table 键。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:58
msgid ""
"Integer path segments select array elements using Lua's 1-based indexing."
msgstr "整数路径段用于选择数组元素，采用 Lua 的 1-based 索引。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:60
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:60"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:71
msgid "ptool.toml.set"
msgstr "ptool.toml.set"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:73
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:73"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:73
msgid "`v0.4.0` - Added composite value writes and numeric path segments."
msgstr "`v0.4.0` - 新增复合值写入和数字路径段。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:77
msgid ""
"`ptool.toml.set(input, path, value)` sets the value at a specified path and "
"returns the updated TOML text."
msgstr "`ptool.toml.set(input, path, value)` 设置指定路径上的值，并返回更新后的 TOML "
"文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:80
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:80"
msgid "`input` (string, required): The TOML text."
msgstr "`input`（string，必填）：TOML 文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:81
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:81"
msgid ""
"`path` ((string|integer)[], required): A non-empty path array, such as `{"
"\"package\", \"version\"}` or `{\"bin\", 1, \"name\"}`."
msgstr ""
"`path`（(string|integer)[]，必填）：非空路径数组，例如 `{\"package\", "
"\"version\"}` 或 `{\"bin\", 1, \"name\"}`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:83
msgid ""
"`value` (string|integer|number|boolean|table, required): The value to write."
msgstr "`value`（string|integer|number|boolean|table，必填）：要写入的值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:84
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:84"
msgid "Returns: The updated TOML string."
msgstr "返回：更新后的 TOML 字符串。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:86
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:86"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:88
msgid "Missing intermediate paths are created automatically as tables."
msgstr "缺失的中间路径会自动创建为 table。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:89
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:89"
msgid "If an intermediate path exists but is not a table, an error is raised."
msgstr "如果某个中间路径已存在但不是 table，会抛出错误。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:90
msgid "Lua tables with only string keys are written as TOML tables."
msgstr "仅包含字符串键的 Lua table 会写成 TOML table。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:91
msgid "Lua sequence tables are written as TOML arrays."
msgstr "Lua 序列表会写成 TOML array。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:92
msgid ""
"A Lua sequence of string-keyed tables is written as a TOML array of tables."
msgstr "由“仅包含字符串键的 Lua table”组成的序列表会写成 TOML array of tables。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:93
msgid "Empty Lua tables are currently written as TOML tables."
msgstr "空 Lua table 目前会按 TOML table 写入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:94
msgid ""
"Parsing and writing back are based on `toml_edit`, which preserves original "
"comments and formatting as much as possible."
msgstr "解析和回写基于 `toml_edit`，会尽可能保留原始注释和格式。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:97
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:97"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:111
msgid "ptool.toml.remove"
msgstr "ptool.toml.remove"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:113
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:113"
msgid "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.1.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:113
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:113"
msgid "`v0.4.0` - Added numeric path segments for array indexing."
msgstr "`v0.4.0` - 新增数组索引用的数字路径段。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:117
msgid ""
"`ptool.toml.remove(input, path)` removes the specified path and returns the "
"updated TOML text."
msgstr "`ptool.toml.remove(input, path)` 删除指定路径，并返回更新后的 TOML 文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:120
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:120"
msgid "`input` (string, required): The TOML text."
msgstr "`input`（string，必填）：TOML 文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:121
msgid ""
"`path` ((string|integer)[], required): A non-empty path array, such as `{"
"\"package\", \"name\"}` or `{\"bin\", 1}`."
msgstr ""
"`path`（(string|integer)[]，必填）：非空路径数组，例如 `{\"package\", "
"\"name\"}` 或 `{\"bin\", 1}`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:123
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:123"
msgid "Returns: The updated TOML string."
msgstr "返回：更新后的 TOML 字符串。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:125
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:125"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:127
msgid ""
"If the path does not exist, no error is raised and the original text "
"(or an equivalent form) is returned."
msgstr "如果路径不存在，不会报错，而是返回原始文本或其等价形式。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:129
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:129"
msgid "If an intermediate path exists but is not a table, an error is raised."
msgstr "如果某个中间路径已存在但不是 table，会抛出错误。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:131
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:131"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:139
msgid "ptool.toml.stringify"
msgstr "ptool.toml.stringify"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:141
msgid "`v0.4.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.4.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:143
msgid "`ptool.toml.stringify(value)` converts a Lua value to TOML text."
msgstr "`ptool.toml.stringify(value)` 将 Lua 值编码为 TOML 文本。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:145
msgid "`value` (table, required): The root TOML table to encode."
msgstr "`value`（table，必填）：要编码的根 TOML table。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:146
msgid "Returns: The encoded TOML string."
msgstr "返回：编码后的 TOML 字符串。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:148
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:148"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:150
msgid "The root value must be a Lua table representing a TOML table."
msgstr "根值必须是表示 TOML table 的 Lua table。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:151
msgid ""
"Nested Lua tables follow the same table/array rules as `ptool.toml.set`."
msgstr "嵌套 Lua table 与 `ptool.toml.set` 使用相同的 table/array 判定规则。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:152
msgid "Empty Lua tables are currently encoded as TOML tables."
msgstr "空 Lua table 目前会编码为 TOML table。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:154
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:154"
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:168
msgid "Notes:"
msgstr "说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:170
msgid ""
"The `path` argument for `ptool.toml.get/set/remove` must be a non-empty "
"array of strings and/or positive integers."
msgstr "`ptool.toml.get/set/remove` 的 `path` 参数必须是由字符串和/或正整数构成的非空"
"数组。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:172
msgid "Integer path segments are 1-based so they match Lua array indexing."
msgstr "整数路径段是 1-based 的，与 Lua 数组索引保持一致。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/toml.md:173
msgid "TOML datetime/date/time values are still read back as Lua strings."
msgstr "TOML datetime/date/time 值目前仍会读取为 Lua string。"
